question:
Quyidagi kodda `Promise.all` ishlatilganda nima yuz beradi?
```javascript
const p1 = Promise.resolve(10);
const p2 = Promise.reject('Xato!');
Promise.all([p1, p2]).catch(err => console.log(err));
```

Quyidagi kod bajarilgandan keyin konsolga nima chiqadi?
```javascript
Promise.resolve('A').then(val => {
  console.log(val);
  return 'B';
}).then(val => {
  console.log(val);
});
```
